{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast to previous techniques, our proposed SK-Tuning method introduces a novel strategy that utilizes authentic, semantically meaningful prompts or prefix texts during adapter training.",
    "This method capitalizes on the zero-shot capabilities of large language models (LLMs) and their fundamental understanding of linguistic semantics.",
    "As a result, SK-Tuning is designed to achieve faster convergence and enhance task performance.",
    "Through extensive experimental evaluations and comprehensive comparative analysis, we establish the superiority of SK-Tuning over existing fine-tuning techniques.",
    "These findings highlight the significant potential of SK-Tuning to advance fine-tuning methodologies in the field of NLP."
  ]
}